text: Jönköpings SS is a Swedish swim team from Jönköping. The team is one of the oldest in Sweden, founded in 1829. They train in Rosenlundsbadet, arena for the 1977 European Aquatics Championships. ==Swimmers== *Eva Berglund *Filip Lundeholm ==External links== *Jönköpings SS's official homepage Category:Swimming clubs in Sweden Category:1829 establishments in Sweden Category:Sports clubs established in the 1820s Category:Sport in Jönköping County Category:Clubs and societies in Sweden
